
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-liyz-trill-reqs-mlt2uni-opt-00.txt'>
    <title>"Requirements for multicast to unicast optimization in Trill", Li Yizhou</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-liyz-trill-reqs-mlt2uni-opt-00.txt</link>
    <description>Instead of always blindly forwarding multicast/broadcast frames through a distribution tree in Trill, some optimizations can be done to convert multicast/broadcast to unicast for certain IP controlling packets. This draft shows the scenarios in which such optimizations are needed.</description>
    <dc:date>2010-07-03T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
